<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whole-n">whole <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /həʊl/    美 /hoʊl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-the-whole-a-whole">1.★ <strong>[用the whole] 全部；全体；[常用a whole] 整体：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some of his ideas are interesting, but <strong>the whole of</strong> it is ridiculous. 
他的一部分想法很有趣，但整体来看很荒谬。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nature is a whole.
自然界是一个统一体。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="as-a-whole">as a whole</h3>
<p>1.<strong>总体上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We must consider these matters as a whole.
我们必须全盘考虑这些事。</p></div>

<h3 id="on-the-whole">on the whole</h3>
<p>1.<strong>总的看来；总体而言：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On the whole the warming of the earth is a phenomenon that causes great concern.
总的说来，地球变暖是一个引起极大关注的现象。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 4</footer></div></div>